-- 2012-05-22T09:18:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-22/gazprom-board-recommends-proposed-dividend-of-8-97-rubles-share.html
OAO Gazprom’s board recommended
shareholders approve the 2011 dividend payment of 8.97 rubles a
share that management proposed in April.  Gazprom,  Russia ’s state-run gas producer and exporter,
commented today in a statement after a board meeting. The
company paid 3.85 rubles a share for 2010, according to data
compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
